---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---
<PageLayout
  title="Shipping — Syvidea"
  description="Shipping and customs information for Syvidea's curated partner workstation options. Serving the US and Canada."
>
  <article class="section">
    <div class="container-page max-w-3xl prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert">
      <h1>Shipping & Customs</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Syvidea coordinates shipping of curated partner workstations to customers in the United States and Canada.
        This page summarizes how shipping, customs, and delivery timing work. Final terms are confirmed in your
        written quote.
      </p>

      <h2>Regions served</h2>
      <p>
        We currently serve customers in the <strong>United States</strong> and <strong>Canada</strong>. For other
        destinations, send a message via the contact form and we will let you know if we can support your shipment.
      </p>

      <h2>Shipping options</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Standard international shipping</strong> — typical lead time, most cost-effective.</li>
        <li><strong>Expedited shipping</strong> — faster delivery at additional cost, subject to availability.</li>
        <li><strong>Freight / pallet shipping</strong> — used for larger orders or specific supply batches.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        The exact shipping option, carrier, and cost are confirmed in your written quote based on the destination
        address and the supply batch of the selected partner brand.
      </p>

      <h2>Customs, duties, and taxes</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>United States:</strong> Import duties and any applicable state sales tax may apply and are the buyer's responsibility unless explicitly included in the quote.</li>
        <li><strong>Canada:</strong> GST/HST/PST/QST and any applicable duties apply and are the buyer's responsibility unless explicitly included in the quote.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We will quote duties and taxes where we can, but final customs treatment is determined by the carrier
        and local customs authority.
      </p>

      <h2>Estimated delivery windows</h2>
      <p>
        Delivery windows depend on the partner brand, configuration, supply batch, and destination. Typical ranges
        are confirmed in the written quote. Supply batch timing can affect delivery windows for specific configurations.
      </p>

      <h2>Tracking</h2>
      <p>
        Once your unit ships, we share the tracking number and the carrier. Status updates are sent by email
        from the Syvidea team.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about shipping, customs, or delivery? <a href="/contact">Send a message</a> and we will respond.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</PageLayout>
